'''''Vici of [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]''''' was a [[Holovid/Legends|holovid]] showcasing information on the lives of [[Vici Ramunee|Vici]] and [[Veni Ramunee]]. It was one of [[Shannon Voorson]]'s favorites. In it, Vici and Veni were fighting large reptiles.<ref name="Slaying">{{JournalCite|9|Slaying Dragons}}</ref>

